---
// Solution Section V2
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-subtle">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-12">
      <!-- Título -->
      <div class="text-center space-y-6 animate-fade-in">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">A Solução</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
          É por isso que criamos o 
          <span class="bg-gradient-hero bg-clip-text text-transparent"> AppConcurso</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          O AppConcurso é a sua resposta definitiva à fragmentação. Atuamos como seu{" "}
          <span class="font-semibold text-foreground">"Cérebro Organizacional"</span>, e nossa{" "}
          <span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Super Inteligência AC</span> é um mentor virtual 
          completo que guia você do zero até a aprovação.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pilares -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 pt-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4 p-6 bg-card rounded-xl border border-border shadow-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-hero rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-glow">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-foreground" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Centralização Total</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Todos os seus cursinhos, editais e materiais em um único lugar organizado.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4 p-6 bg-card rounded-xl border border-border shadow-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-hero rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-glow">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-foreground" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">IA Personalizada</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Plano de estudos adaptado às suas necessidades e pontos fracos específicos.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4 p-6 bg-card rounded-xl border border-border shadow-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-hero rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-glow">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-foreground" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Foco no que Importa</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Identifique e trabalhe exatamente no que cai na prova, sem dispersão.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center pt-8">
        <a 
          href="#hero" 
          class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-all hover:shadow-lg active:scale-95"
        >
          Comece Grátis Agora
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
